This is the correlator_cc-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the correlator_cc blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'correlator_cc', which is imported as:

    import correlator_cc

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using: 

    help(correlator_cc)
